1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:04,000
In medical research, evidence is the foundation.

2
00:00:04,200 --> 00:00:09,000
MedEvidence AI — Your intelligent evidence-based medicine search assistant.

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:16,500
Clinical decisions require evidence-based support.

4
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:21,000
But facing massive medical literature, have you ever wondered —

5
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:25,000
How to classify evidence levels?

6
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:29,000
How to quickly search Chinese and English literature?

7
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:33,000
Where are the high-quality studies?

8
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:40,000
MedEvidence AI, powered by KnowS evidence-based database

9
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:44,500
and StepFun large language model, provides you with

10
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:49,000
Bilingual intelligent literature search,

11
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:53,000
5-level evidence grading,

12
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:58,000
and one-stop AI-generated clinical summaries.

13
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:54,000
Let's try a Chinese search.

14
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:58,500
Enter "Meta分析 抗生素" (Meta-analysis antibiotics),

15
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:03,000
the system automatically calls the Chinese literature database,

16
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:07,000
returning the most relevant research results.

17
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:12,000
As you can see, all 5 results are accurately identified as Level 1

18
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:16,500
— Meta-analysis or systematic review,

19
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:21,500
the highest level of evidence in evidence-based medicine.

20
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:27,000
No more manual study type classification —

21
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:30,000
the system does it for you.

22
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:34,500
English search is equally precise.

23
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,500
Search "COVID-19 vaccine randomized trial",

24
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:44,500
the system returns multiple high-quality RCTs,

25
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:49,000
all marked as Level 1.

26
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:54,000
Each paper includes journal name, impact factor,

27
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:58,500
DOI, publication date, and more,

28
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:03,500
helping you quickly assess quality and access the full text.

29
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:09,000
What is the 5-level evidence grading system?

30
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:13,000
From Level 5: case reports and expert opinions,

31
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:17,500
to Level 4: case series and clinical guidelines,

32
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:22,000
Level 3: cohort and case-control studies,

33
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:26,500
then Level 2: lower-quality randomized controlled trials,

34
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:30,500
and the highest Level 1

35
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:34,000
— Meta-analysis and high-quality RCTs.

36
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:38,000
Higher evidence level means more reliable results.

37
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:44,500
Technically, MedEvidence AI is built on FastAPI,

38
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:49,500
deeply integrated with KnowS evidence-based database

39
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:53,000
and StepFun large language model.

40
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:57,500
Supports one-click deployment on ModelScope,

41
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:01,000
Docker container deployment,

42
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:04,000
and local execution — fully open source.

43
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:09,000
We prioritize medical safety and compliance.

44
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:13,000
This tool does not use real patient data,

45
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:16,500
does not provide diagnostic advice,

46
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:20,000
and is for medical research and learning only.

47
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:24,000
Please follow medical advice for clinical decisions.

48
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:28,000
MedEvidence AI,

49
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:32,500
illuminating every corner of medical research with AI.

50
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:37,000
Try it now and start your intelligent evidence journey.
